name: Cajsa Wessberg Embedding
description:
Check out for more -- Ko-Fi 

A Stable Diffusion Embedding.

Instructions:

To be used on Automatic1111's WebUI. Place it in your "embeddings" folder in the WebUI root folder.

Call it out in your prompt with the file name "cajwes".

Weighting for the embed can be adjusted by "(cajwes:0.9)"

0.9~1 is the recommended weighting.

Your output will vary depending upon your prompt, negative prompt, model, VAE, and Hypernetworks used.
